title: Avitus - 🧷・about
html:
**What is Avitus?**

Avitus is the first-ever modular and permissionless perpetual dex protocol custom-built on Movement Labs. It allows any asset to be utilized as collateral for perpetual futures trading, finally empowering all asset holders to unlock more utility from their portfolios.  

**Test out our features on the live testnet at  ** **https://testnet.avituslabs.xyz/#/trade**
